OKPF is an open standard for packaging structured human expertise.
The specification, schemas, reference implementations, tooling, and
documentation in this repository are the work of the OKPF contributors.

The examples/ directory contains example knowledge packs licensed under
Creative Commons Attribution 4.0 International (CC-BY-4.0), as declared
in each example's license.json file.

---

This project does not include any third-party code or content at this time.
Third-party dependencies used by the reference implementations are listed
in their respective package manifests (pyproject.toml, package.json) and
are not part of the OKPF specification.

